                <p><strong>Step 1</strong>: Download <a href="https://pkc.sw556.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">PKC App</a> at URL: <a href="https://invite.30co.cn/pkc.php?code=563L5&amp;v=1558233267">https://invite.30co.cn/pkc.php?code=563L5&amp;v=1558233267</a>. Click the green DOWNLOAD button. Note: If you are not able to download by “Get it for Android or IOS”, please use the Download 1 or Download 2</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-697 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-1-300x275.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="275" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-697 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20275%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-1-300x275.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="275" /></p>
                <p>Note: iOS users may encounter the following popup when launching PKC (for the first time)</p>
                <p><strong>Step 2</strong>: Click on Cancel to proceed</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-698" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-2-300x251.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="251" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-698" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20251%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-2-300x251.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="251" /></p>
                <p><strong>Step 3</strong>: Follow these steps to trust the PKC app on your iOS device.</p>
                <p>1. Go to Settings</p>
                <p>2. Select General</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-699" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-3-300x244.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="244" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-699" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20244%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-3-300x244.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="244" /></p>
                <p>3. Select Device Management BRAIN CLUSTERS INFOTECH PRIVATE</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-700" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-4-300x274.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="274" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-700" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20274%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-4-300x274.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="274" /></p>
                <p>4. Select: Trust “BRAIN CLUSTERS INFOTECH PRIVA…”</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-701" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-5-224x300.jpg" alt="" width="224" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-701" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20224%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-5-224x300.jpg" alt="" width="224" height="300" /></p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <h2>Create a PKC account</h2>
                <p>1. Launch the PKC app. You will be prompted to accept PKC notifications</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-702" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-6-190x300.jpg" alt="" width="190" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-702" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20190%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-6-190x300.jpg" alt="" width="190" height="300" /></p>
                <p>2. Select Register to create a PKC account</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-703" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-7-165x300.jpg" alt="" width="165" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-703" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20165%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-7-165x300.jpg" alt="" width="165" height="300" /></p>
                <p>3. Enter your invite code (Get the invite code from your Community Head or Agent)</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-704" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-8-173x300.jpg" alt="" width="173" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-704" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20173%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-8-173x300.jpg" alt="" width="173" height="300" /></p>
                <p>4. Select country code US+1 and enter your mobile number</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-705" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-9-182x300.jpg" alt="" width="182" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-705" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20182%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-9-182x300.jpg" alt="" width="182" height="300" /></p>
                <p>5. Enter verification code, then click on Next</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-706" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-10-185x300.jpg" alt="" width="185" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-706" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20185%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-10-185x300.jpg" alt="" width="185" height="300" /></p>
                <p>6. Verification code will be sent via text message</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-707 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-11-300x292.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="292" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-707 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20292%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-11-300x292.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="292" /></p>
                <p>7. Retrieve verification code sent to your mobile phone</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-708 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-12-300x111.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="111" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-708 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20111%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-12-300x111.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="111" /></p>
                <p>8. Enter the code, then click on Next</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-709 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-13-211x300.jpg" alt="" width="211" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-709 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20211%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-13-211x300.jpg" alt="" width="211" height="300" /></p>
                <p>9. Create nickname (name that is displayed for other players to see), password, confirm password, then click on Next</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-710 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-14-218x300.jpg" alt="" width="218" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-710 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20218%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-14-218x300.jpg" alt="" width="218" height="300" /></p>
                <p>10. Create username (this is your login ID you will use to log into the app), re-enter username, then click on Next</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-711 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-15-200x300.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-711 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20200%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/download-register-15-200x300.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="300" /></p>
            </div>
