        <div id="popmake-493" class="pum-container popmake theme-423 pum-responsive pum-responsive-medium responsive size-medium">
            <div class="pum-content popmake-content">
                <h2>Deposit via Coinmama</h2>
                <p><strong>1. Coinmama registration</strong></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;"><strong>NOTE:</strong> Quickest way to get purchased bitcoin onto PKC (no hold period)</p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">a. Set up a <a href="https://www.coinmama.com/signup" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Coinmama</a> account. Fill out the required information and click on Create Account</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-675 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1-coinmama-248x300.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-675 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20248%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1-coinmama-248x300.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="300" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">b. Verify account</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-676 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/2-coinmama-300x180.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="180" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-676 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20180%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/2-coinmama-300x180.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="180" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">c. Confirm your email</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-677 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/3-coinmama-300x210.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="210" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-677 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20210%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/3-coinmama-300x210.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="210" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">d. Welcome to Coinmama. Click on Continue to proceed to the validation process</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-678 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/4-coinmama-173x300.jpg" alt="" width="173" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-678 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20173%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/4-coinmama-173x300.jpg" alt="" width="173" height="300" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">e. You will need to complete the short Coinmama validation process to purchase bitcoin (Steps you may see)</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-679 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/5-coinmama-300x197.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="197" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-679 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20197%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/5-coinmama-300x197.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="197" /></p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-680 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/6-coinmama-300x201.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="201" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-680 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20201%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/6-coinmama-300x201.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="201" /></p>
                <p><strong>2. Create deposit request on PKC</strong></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">a. Log into PKC and click on the +</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-681 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/7-coinmama-300x267.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="267" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-681 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20267%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/7-coinmama-300x267.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="267" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">b. Select BTC</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-682 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/8-coinmama-300x115.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="115" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-682 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20115%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/8-coinmama-300x115.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="115" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">c. Enter amount (in RMB) to be deposited to PKC. Example: 777, then click on next step</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-683 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/9-coinmama-280x300.jpg" alt="" width="280" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-683 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20280%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/9-coinmama-280x300.jpg" alt="" width="280" height="300" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">d. Confirm Order Info</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-684 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/10-coinmama-300x282.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="282" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-684 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20282%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/10-coinmama-300x282.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="282" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">e. IMPORTANT: 1) The BTC amount (0.03443955) must be exact or your deposit will be delay. 2) Copy the PKC wallet address to paste into your Coinmama (Address to send to:).</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-685 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/11-coinmama-300x265.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="265" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-685 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20265%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/11-coinmama-300x265.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="265" /></p>
                <p><strong>3. Buy BTC to deposit into PKC</strong></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">a. Log into <a href="https://www.coinmama.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Coinmama</a>, click on the menu (to right) or Buy Coins</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-686 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/12-coinmama-297x300.jpg" alt="" width="297" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-686 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20297%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/12-coinmama-297x300.jpg" alt="" width="297" height="300" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">b. Enter your Coinmama Email and password to log in</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-687 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/13-coinmama-238x300.jpg" alt="" width="238" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-687 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20238%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/13-coinmama-238x300.jpg" alt="" width="238" height="300" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">c. To buy bitcoins, click on Buy</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-688 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/14-coinmama-300x160.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="160" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-688 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20160%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/14-coinmama-300x160.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="160" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">d. Click on Bitcoin</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-689 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/15-coinmama-300x167.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="167" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-689 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20167%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/15-coinmama-300x167.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="167" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">e. You can purchase BTC with a specific amount using the numeric keypad (scroll down to bottom of page)</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-690 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/16-coinmama-176x300.jpg" alt="" width="176" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-690 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20176%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/16-coinmama-176x300.jpg" alt="" width="176" height="300" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">f. Paste the PKC wallet address into the Coinmama Bitcoin Address field, then click on Go to Payment.
                    <br /> <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>NOTE:</strong> *IT IS CRITICAL THAT THIS ADDRESS IS COPIED CORRECTLY FOR YOUR BITCOIN TO BE DEPOSITED IN THE CORRECT ACCOUNT.</span></p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-691 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/17-coinmama-193x300.jpg" alt="" width="193" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-691 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20193%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/17-coinmama-193x300.jpg" alt="" width="193" height="300" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">g. Add debit or credit card information, then click on Pay Now</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-692 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/18-coinmama-167x300.jpg" alt="" width="167" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-692 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20167%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/18-coinmama-167x300.jpg" alt="" width="167" height="300" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">h. Confirm wallet address by confirming Email sent by Coinmama</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-693 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/19-coinmama-300x183.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="183" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-693 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20183%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/19-coinmama-300x183.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="183" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">i. Confirm wallet address where Coinmama will send BTC to</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-694 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/20-coinmama-300x285.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="285" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-694 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20285%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/20-coinmama-300x285.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="285" /></p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">j. Confirm wallet address by confirming Email sent by Coinmama. Now just wait for the funds to show up in your PKC account.</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-695 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/21-coinmama-300x216.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="216" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-695 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20216%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/21-coinmama-300x216.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="216" /></p>
            </div>
            <button type="button" class="pum-close popmake-close" aria-label="Close"> × </button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="pum-495" class="pum pum-overlay pum-theme-423 pum-theme-lightbox popmake-overlay pum-click-to-close click_open" data-popmake="{&quot;id&quot;:495,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;deposit-via-coinbase&quot;,&quot;theme_id&quot;:423,&quot;cookies&quot;:[],&quot;triggers&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;click_open&quot;,&quot;settings&quot;:{&quot;extra_selectors&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cookie_name&quot;:null}}],&quot;mobile_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;tablet_disabled&quot;:null,&quot;meta&quot;:{&quot;display&quot;:{&quot;stackable&quot;:false,&quot;overlay_disabled&quot;:false,&quot;scrollable_content&quot;:false,&quot;disable_reposition&quot;:false,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width&quot;:&quot;0%&quot;,&quot;responsive_min_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;responsive_max_width&quot;:&quot;600px&quot;,&quot;responsive_max_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_width&quot;:&quot;640px&quot;,&quot;custom_width_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height&quot;:&quot;380px&quot;,&quot;custom_height_unit&quot;:false,&quot;custom_height_auto&quot;:false,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;position_from_trigger&quot;:false,&quot;position_top&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;position_left&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_bottom&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_right&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;position_fixed&quot;:false,&quot;animation_type&quot;:&quot;fade&quot;,&quot;animation_speed&quot;:&quot;350&quot;,&quot;animation_origin&quot;:&quot;center top&quot;,&quot;overlay_zindex&quot;:false,&quot;zindex&quot;:&quot;1999999999&quot;},&quot;close&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;button_delay&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;overlay_click&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;esc_press&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;f4_press&quot;:false},&quot;click_open&quot;:[]}}" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
        <div id="popmake-495" class="pum-container popmake theme-423 pum-responsive pum-responsive-medium responsive size-medium">
            <div class="pum-content popmake-content">
                <h2>Deposit via Coinbase</h2>
                <p><strong>NOTE</strong>: Use your debit card to avoid a waiting period to transfer bitcoin. There maybe a 5-7 days waiting period to transfer the bitcoin you purchased depending on form of payment (i.e. wire transfer or credit card)</p>
                <p>a. Set up a <a href="https://www.coinbase.com/signup" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Coinbase</a> account. Fill out the required information and click on Create Account</p>
                <p>b. Coinbase will send an Email for you to confirm</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-647 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1-coinbase-246x300.jpg" alt="" width="246" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-647 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20246%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1-coinbase-246x300.jpg" alt="" width="246" height="300" /></p>
                <p>c. Verify your Email address</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-648 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/2-coinbase-300x217.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="217" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-648 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20217%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/2-coinbase-300x217.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="217" /></p>
                <p>d. Add phone number</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-649 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/3-coinbase-208x300.jpg" alt="" width="208" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-649 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20208%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/3-coinbase-208x300.jpg" alt="" width="208" height="300" /></p>
                <p>e. Text verification code to your mobile phone</p>
                <p>f. Entered the required information and submit</p>
                <p>g. Verify your identity</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-650 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/4-coinbase-243x300.jpg" alt="" width="243" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-650 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20243%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/4-coinbase-243x300.jpg" alt="" width="243" height="300" /></p>
                <p>h. Upload driver license info.</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-651 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/5-coinbase-272x300.jpg" alt="" width="272" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-651 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20272%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/5-coinbase-272x300.jpg" alt="" width="272" height="300" /></p>
                <p>i. Add deposit methods (Debit or Credit Card)</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-652 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/6-coinbase-219x300.jpg" alt="" width="219" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-652 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20219%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/6-coinbase-219x300.jpg" alt="" width="219" height="300" /></p>
                <p>j. Log into <a href="https://www.coinbase.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Coinbase</a> to buy bitcoin. Click on the menu (top right)</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-653 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/7-coinbase-300x221.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="221" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-653 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20221%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/7-coinbase-300x221.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="221" /></p>
                <p>k. Sign into Coinbase</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="wp-image-654 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/8-coinbase-300x236.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="236" /></noscript><img class="lazyload wp-image-654 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20236%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/8-coinbase-300x236.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="236" /></p>
                <p>l. Click on Accounts</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-655 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/9-coinbase-300x66.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="66" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-655 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%2066%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/9-coinbase-300x66.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="66" /></p>
                <p>m. Select BTC wallet</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-656 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/10-coinbase-139x300.jpg" alt="" width="139" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-656 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20139%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/10-coinbase-139x300.jpg" alt="" width="139" height="300" /></p>
                <p>n. Select Buy</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-657 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/11-coinbase-300x244.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="244" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-657 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20244%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/11-coinbase-300x244.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="244" /></p>
                <p>o. Enter your purchase amount and select what payment method you’d like to use.</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-658 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/12-coinbase-150x300.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-658 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20150%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/12-coinbase-150x300.jpg" alt="" width="150" height="300" /></p>
                <p>p. Confirm purchase</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-659 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/13-coinbase-193x300.jpg" alt="" width="193" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-659 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20193%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/13-coinbase-193x300.jpg" alt="" width="193" height="300" /></p>
                <p>q. Verify your identity</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-660 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/14-coinbase-300x239.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="239" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-660 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20239%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/14-coinbase-300x239.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="239" /></p>
                <p><strong>5. Coinbase to PKC</strong></p>
                <p>a. Log into PKC, clickon Funds</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-661 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/15-coinbase-300x48.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="48" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-661 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%2048%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/15-coinbase-300x48.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="48" /></p>
                <p>b. Click on Funds</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-662 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/16-coinbase-300x91.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="91" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-662 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%2091%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/16-coinbase-300x91.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="91" /></p>
                <p>c. Clickon BTC</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-663 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/17-coinbase-300x122.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="122" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-663 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20122%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/17-coinbase-300x122.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="122" /></p>
                <p>d. Enter amount you like to deposit in RMB, then click on next step</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-664 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/18-coinbase-300x263.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="263" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-664 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20263%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/18-coinbase-300x263.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="263" /></p>
                <p>e. Enter your PKC userID, then click on confirm</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-665 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/19-coinbase-300x226.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="226" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-665 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20226%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/19-coinbase-300x226.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="226" /></p>
                <p>f. PKC Deposit Slip</p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">1. Copy down the BTC amount exactly</p>
                <p style="padding-left: 40px;">2. Copy the PKC wallet address to enter into Coinbase</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-666 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/20-coinbase-300x265.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="265" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-666 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20265%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/20-coinbase-300x265.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="265" /></p>
                <p>g. Log into Coinbase</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-667 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/21-coinbase-300x226.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="226" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-667 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20226%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/21-coinbase-300x226.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="226" /></p>
                <p>h. Click on Bitcoin</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-668 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/22-coinbase-300x256.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="256" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-668 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20256%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/22-coinbase-300x256.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="256" /></p>
                <p>i. Click on BTC Wallet</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-669 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/23-coinbase-300x54.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="54" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-669 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%2054%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/23-coinbase-300x54.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="54" /></p>
                <p>j. Click on Send Bitcoin (airplane icon)</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-670 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/24-coinbase-300x69.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="69" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-670 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%2069%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/24-coinbase-300x69.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="69" /></p>
                <p>k. Enter the exact bitcoin amount ex. 0.02983338 from f. (PKC Deposit Slip). <strong>NOTE:</strong> If this btc amount is not exact, it may delay your deposit ontoPKC</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-671 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/25-coinbase-159x300.jpg" alt="" width="159" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-671 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20159%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/25-coinbase-159x300.jpg" alt="" width="159" height="300" /></p>
                <p>l. Coinbase transaction fee. Review and Confirm.</p>
                <p>
                    <noscript><img class="size-medium wp-image-672 aligncenter" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/26-coinbase-300x187.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="187" /></noscript><img class="lazyload size-medium wp-image-672 aligncenter" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20187%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/26-coinbase-300x187.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="187" /></p>
            </div>
