        <div id="popmake-497" class="pum-container popmake theme-423 pum-responsive pum-responsive-medium responsive size-medium">
            <div class="pum-content popmake-content">
                <h2 class="p1">PKC Referral Rewards System</h2>
                <p><strong>1. Invite Your Friends: PKC offers a referral rewards system where you may earn up to 30% of the rake of any non professional player that you sign-up to PKC using your custom referral code</strong></p>
                <p>1. Retrieve your Invite Code by going to Profile</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone wp-image-715 size-medium" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/referral-rewards-system-1-300x52.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="52" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone wp-image-715 size-medium" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%2052%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/referral-rewards-system-1-300x52.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="52" /></p>
                <p>2. Select Invite Friends</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-716" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/referral-rewards-system-2-300x91.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="91" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-716" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%2091%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/referral-rewards-system-2-300x91.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="91" /></p>
                <p>3. Click on Invite Code</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-717" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/referral-rewards-system-3-300x227.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="227" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-717" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20227%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/referral-rewards-system-3-300x227.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="227" /></p>
                <p>4. Send invite code along with PKC download link to new player. NOTE: this code is case sensitive</p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <p><strong>2. Player referral redemption</strong></p>
                <p>A. Log into back end portal using the same login as PKC: <a href="https://user.237u.cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">PKC portal login</a></p>
                <p>B. Switch language to English (top right corner)</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-718" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/referral-rewards-system-4-300x224.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="224" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-718" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20224%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/referral-rewards-system-4-300x224.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="224" /></p>
                <p>C. Use your PKC login</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-719" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/referral-rewards-system-5-300x139.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="139" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-719" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20300%20139%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/referral-rewards-system-5-300x139.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="139" /></p>
                <p>D. Check your Income Available and press Receive</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <noscript><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-720" src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/referral-rewards-system-6-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /></noscript><img class="lazyload alignnone size-medium wp-image-720" src='data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20viewBox=%220%200%20225%20300%22%3E%3C/svg%3E' data-src="https://pkcusa.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/referral-rewards-system-6-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /></p>
                <p>E. The money you redeem is instantly available in your player account.</p>
            </div>
